</div>

<$reveal stateTitle={{{[statewrap-ref[tab]]}}} type="match" text="overview">

!! Overview

Task ''<$text text={{{[statewrap-get[task]]}}}/>'' in project ''<$text text={{{[statewrap-get[project]]}}}/>''.

This is the overview panel. In a real app, this would show task details, assignees, deadlines, and status.

</$reveal>

<$reveal stateTitle={{{[statewrap-ref[tab]]}}} type="match" text="notes">

!! Notes

Notes for ''<$text text={{{[statewrap-get[task]]}}}/>''.

This is the notes panel. In a real app, this would show editable notes and comments.

</$reveal>

<$reveal stateTitle={{{[statewrap-ref[tab]]}}} type="match" text="log">

!! Activity Log

Activity log for ''<$text text={{{[statewrap-get[task]]}}}/>''.

This is the activity log panel. In a real app, this would show a timeline of changes and events.

